quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  73,1,ae ( Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) jo kapray mein lapat rahay ho
  73,2,raat ko qiyamkiya karo magar thori si raat
  73,3,( qiyam ) aadhi raat (kiya karo )
  73,4,ya is se kuch kam ya kuch ziyada aur quran ko thehr thehr kar parha karo
  73,5,hum anqareeb tum par aik bhaari farmaan nazil karen ge
  73,6,kuch shak nahi ke raat ka uthna ( nafs behimi ) ko sakht pamaal karta hai aur is waqt zikar bhi khoob durust hota hai
  73,7,din ke waqt to tumhe aur bohat se shugal hotay hain
  73,8,to apne perwar-digaar ke naam ka zikar karo aur har taraf se be talluq ho kar isi ki taraf mutwajjah hojao
  73,9,mashriq aur maghrib ka maalik ( hai aur ) is ke siwa koi mabood nahi to isi ko apna karsaaz banaao
  73,10,aur jo jo ( dil azaar ) baatein yeh log kehte hain un ko sahte raho aur achay tareeq se un se kinara kash raho
  73,11,aur mujhe un jhutlanay walon se jo doltmnd hain samajh lainay do aur un ko thori si mohlat day do
  73,12,kuch shak nahi ke hamaray paas berriyan hain aur bharakti hui aag hai
  73,13,aur glugeer khana hai aur dard dainay wala azaab ( bhi ) hai
  73,14,jis din zameen aur pahar kanpnay lagen aur pahar aisay bhar bharay ( goya ) rait ke teele ho jaien
  73,15,( ae ahal mecca ) jis terhan hum ne firaon ke paas ( moose ko ) paighambar ( bana kar ) bheja tha ( isi terhan ) tumahray paas bhi ( Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) rasool beje hain jo tumahray muqablay mein gawah hon ge
  73,16,so firaon ne ( hamaray ) paighambar ka kaha nah maana to hum ne is ko barray wabaal mein pakar liya
  73,17,agar tum bhi ( un payghambaroon ko ) nah manu ge to is din se kyonkr bachcho ge jo bachon ko boorha kar day ga
  73,18,( aur ) jis se aasman phatt jaye ga. yeh is ka wada ( poora ) ho kar rahay ga
  73,19,yeh ( quran ) to nasiyaat hai. so jo chahay apne perwar-digaar taq ( pounchanay ka ) rasta ikhtiyar karle
